attributionInfo.agentName: Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection
Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection

description: Stately South Boston Brownstone situated in the heart of all that the highly sought after City Point location has to offer. Walking distance to the beach, Castle Island, M St Park, shops, restaurants, schools and public transport.  The sundrenched open floor plan and high ceilings of this grand home are ideal for entertaining.  Amenities include: a chef's kitchen with granite counters, SS appliances, custom cabinets & a center island.  Just off the kitchen is an oversized deck with stairs to the patio & 2 car parking. This home offers two oversized bedrooms with plenty of closet space, storage & an updated full bath.  There is also a massive floor though primary suite with walk-in closet, classic 3-piece bath, plenty of room for a home office & exercise space.  A magnificent private roof deck provides spectacular city & water views.  This home's lower level has 2 rooms, 1 full bath, a kitchen, great ceiling height, full-size windows & direct access to a patio.
